snippet.title: SimHealth gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for SimHealth, Dos PC game produced by Maxis Software in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/simhealth/8162/
Exploring the interface and playing the political game in this complex health sim.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
